---
import ToolLayout from '../../components/tools/ToolLayout.astro';
import { findTool } from '../../data/tools';

const tool = findTool('eras-protocol');
---

<ToolLayout tool={tool}>
  <aside class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 bg-amber-50 p-5 mb-6 text-sm chinese-line-height">
    <p class="font-bold text-amber-900 mb-1">⚠️ 臨床決策支援工具</p>
    <p class="text-amber-900">
      此工具依 ERAS Society 2018/2023 指引與 ASA 2017 禁食指引整理。
      <strong>實際禁食時間、碳水負荷、藥物調整須以您的麻醉醫師、外科醫師術前說明為準</strong>。
      此工具供患者預備、衛教使用,可列印帶到術前評估討論。
    </p>
  </aside>

  <form id="eras-form" class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 space-y-6 print:hidden">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 font-headline">輸入資料</h2>

    <div>
      <label for="procedureType" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">手術 / 介入類型</label>
      <select id="procedureType" name="procedureType" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 bg-white focus:border-primary focus:outline-none">
        <option value="">— 請選擇 —</option>
        <option value="colonoscopy">無痛大腸鏡(含瀉劑準備)</option>
        <option value="gastroscopy">無痛胃鏡 / 上消化道內視鏡</option>
        <option value="laparoscopic">腹腔鏡手術(膽囊 / 闌尾 / 疝氣)</option>
        <option value="colorectal">大腸直腸手術</option>
        <option value="general">一般外科 / 婦科 / 泌尿科</option>
        <option value="cardiac">心臟血管手術</option>
        <option value="orthopedic">骨科手術(置換 / 脊椎)</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <div>
      <label for="surgeryDateTime" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">預定手術時間(含時間)</label>
      <input type="datetime-local" id="surgeryDateTime" name="surgeryDateTime" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 focus:border-primary focus:outline-none">
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">患者狀況(勾選所有適用)</p>
      <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" name="cond" value="diabetes"> 糖尿病(任何型)</label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" name="cond" value="severe-gerd"> 嚴重胃食道逆流(GERD)</label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" name="cond" value="gastroparesis"> 胃排空延遲 / 胃輕癱</label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" name="cond" value="bariatric"> 過去減重手術(bypass / sleeve)</label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" name="cond" value="glp1"> 正在使用 GLP-1(Wegovy / Ozempic / Mounjaro 等)</label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" name="cond" value="metformin"> 服用 metformin 且手術含顯影劑</label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" name="cond" value="frail"> 高齡 / 衰弱(frailty)</label>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" name="cond" value="emergency"> 急診手術</label>
      </div>
    </div>

    <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-primary text-on-primary font-bold py-3 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
      產生個人化 ERAS 時程
    </button>
  </form>

  <div id="eras-result" class="hidden mt-6"></div>

  <article class="max-w-none mt-10 print:hidden space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-950 font-headline">什麼是 ERAS ?</h2>
    <p class="chinese-line-height text-slate-700">
      <strong>ERAS(Enhanced Recovery After Surgery,加速術後恢復)</strong>是 1997 年丹麥外科醫師 Henrik Kehlet 提出的多模式術前/術中/術後照護整合策略,
      目前已有 ERAS Society 為各類手術發布 20+ 個指引。其核心理念是<strong>用實證打破過去「術前長時間禁食、術後臥床、晚進食」</strong>的傳統,
      改用<strong>術前 2 小時清流質、2 小時碳水負荷、術後早期口進食與早期活動</strong>,證實可縮短住院天數 30%、降低併發症 20%。
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mt-6">ASA 2017 禁食指引(健康成人,選擇性手術)</h3>
    <ul class="chinese-line-height text-slate-700 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm">
      <li><strong>清流質(水、無渣果汁、運動飲料、黑咖啡)</strong>:麻醉前 2 小時即可</li>
      <li><strong>母乳</strong>:麻醉前 4 小時</li>
      <li><strong>嬰兒配方奶、非人類乳</strong>:麻醉前 6 小時</li>
      <li><strong>輕食(吐司 + 清飲料)</strong>:麻醉前 6 小時</li>
      <li><strong>正餐 / 油炸 / 肉類</strong>:麻醉前 8 小時</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mt-6">何時不適用「2 小時清流質」?</h3>
    <ul class="chinese-line-height text-slate-700 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm">
      <li>胃排空延遲(胃輕癱、嚴重 GERD、過去減重手術)</li>
      <li>正在使用 GLP-1 受體促效劑(延緩胃排空)</li>
      <li>胃流出阻塞、急診手術、創傷</li>
      <li>糖尿病嚴重血糖控制不良(自主神經病變導致胃輕癱)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mt-6">主要參考文獻</h3>
    <ul class="chinese-line-height text-slate-700 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm">
      <li>Gustafsson UO, et al. Guidelines for Perioperative Care in Elective Colorectal Surgery: ERAS Society Recommendations 2018. <em>World J Surg</em>. 2019;43:659.</li>
      <li>Practice Guidelines for Preoperative Fasting (ASA 2017). <em>Anesthesiology</em>. 2017;126(3):376.</li>
      <li>Smith MD, et al. Preoperative Carbohydrate Treatment for Enhancing Recovery After Elective Surgery. <em>Cochrane Database</em>. 2014.</li>
      <li>Joshi GP, et al. Perioperative Management of Patients on GLP-1 Receptor Agonists. <em>Anesthesiology</em>. 2024.</li>
    </ul>
  </article>

  <script is:inline>
    const form = document.getElementById('eras-form');
    const result = document.getElementById('eras-result');

    const procedureLabel = {
      'colonoscopy': '無痛大腸鏡',
      'gastroscopy': '無痛胃鏡',
      'laparoscopic': '腹腔鏡手術',
      'colorectal': '大腸直腸手術',
      'general': '一般外科 / 婦科 / 泌尿',
      'cardiac': '心臟血管手術',
      'orthopedic': '骨科手術',
    };

    function fmtDT(d) {
      return d.toLocaleString('zh-TW', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric', weekday: 'short', hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit', hour12: false });
    }

    function fmtTime(d) {
      return d.toLocaleString('zh-TW', { month: 'numeric', day: 'numeric', weekday: 'short', hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit', hour12: false });
    }

    function subHours(d, h) {
      const n = new Date(d);
      n.setHours(n.getHours() - h);
      return n;
    }

    function subDays(d, days) {
      const n = new Date(d);
      n.setDate(n.getDate() - days);
      return n;
    }

    form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      const procedureType = form.procedureType.value;
      const dt = form.surgeryDateTime.value ? new Date(form.surgeryDateTime.value) : null;
      const conds = Array.from(form.querySelectorAll('input[name="cond"]:checked')).map(c => c.value);

      if (!procedureType || !dt) {
        result.innerHTML = '<div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-red-500 bg-red-50 p-4 text-red-900">請選擇手術類型並輸入手術時間。</div>';
        result.classList.remove('hidden');
        return;
      }

      const hasGastricRisk = conds.includes('severe-gerd') || conds.includes('gastroparesis') || conds.includes('bariatric') || conds.includes('glp1');
      const hasDM = conds.includes('diabetes');
      const isEndoscopy = procedureType === 'colonoscopy' || procedureType === 'gastroscopy';
      const needsBowelPrep = procedureType === 'colonoscopy' || procedureType === 'colorectal';

      // 關鍵時點
      const solidCutoff = subHours(dt, hasGastricRisk ? 8 : 6);    // 高風險用 8 小時
      const clearLiquidCutoff = subHours(dt, hasGastricRisk ? 6 : 2); // 高風險改用 6 小時
      const carbLoadTime = subHours(dt, 2);                          // 術前 2h carb load
      const arrivalTime = subHours(dt, 2);                           // 報到時間

      // 碳水負荷適用條件
      const carbLoadEligible = !hasGastricRisk && !conds.includes('emergency') && (!hasDM || procedureType !== 'cardiac');

      // 飲食調整
      let dietBefore;
      if (needsBowelPrep) {
        dietBefore = '檢查前 3 天低渣飲食 → 前 1 天無渣流質 → 依清腸藥指示時程服用';
      } else if (procedureType === 'colorectal' || procedureType === 'laparoscopic') {
        dietBefore = '前 1 天可正常飲食(無低渣需求);術前 6–8 小時起禁固體';
      } else {
        dietBefore = '前 1 天可正常飲食;術前依下方時程禁食禁水';
      }

      // 藥物調整建議
      const medAdjust = [];
      if (conds.includes('metformin')) medAdjust.push('Metformin(伏糖錠 / 美爾胰錠 / 高糖優美等)+ 含顯影劑檢查:手術當日與次日停用,以免乳酸中毒。');
      if (hasDM) medAdjust.push('糖尿病用藥:長效胰島素手術當日減量為 50–70% 平常劑量;短效胰島素手術當日不施打;口服降血糖藥手術當日早上停用。');
      if (conds.includes('glp1')) medAdjust.push('GLP-1(Wegovy / Ozempic / Mounjaro 等):週注射型至少停 1 週、日注射停手術當日。詳見「GLP-1 術前停藥計算器」。');
      medAdjust.push('血壓藥:多數可繼續服用(配少量水);ACEI/ARB 視麻醉計畫可能停手術當日。');
      medAdjust.push('抗血小板 / 抗凝血藥:依藥物與手術出血風險決定。詳見「抗凝血藥停藥工具」。');

      // ERAS bundle
      const erasBundle = [
        '術前衛教:讓您理解整個流程,降低焦慮 → 縮短住院',
        '預防低體溫:術中保溫 + 入手術室前加溫毯(目標 ≥ 36°C)',
        '預防 PONV(術後噁心嘔吐):多模式止吐(Ondansetron + Dexamethasone ± Scopolamine)',
        '多模式止痛:減少 opioid 用量(Acetaminophen + NSAIDs + 區域麻醉)',
        '術中限制性輸液:goal-directed 而非大量輸液',
        '預防 VTE:機械(壓力襪 / IPC)+ 藥物(LMWH,依出血風險)',
        '術後早期口進食:意識清楚即可清流質、能耐受則進到一般飲食',
        '術後早期下床:手術當天或隔天即起身(目標 2 小時/天活動)',
        '早期拔除尿管 / 引流管:避免不必要的「管路綁住病人」',
      ];

      const dietHtml = `
        <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-xs">前1天</span><div>
            <div class="font-bold text-blue-950">${fmtTime(subDays(dt, 1))} 起</div>
            <div class="text-slate-700 mt-1">${dietBefore}</div>
          </div></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-xs">固體</span><div>
            <div class="font-bold text-blue-950">${fmtTime(solidCutoff)} 起禁食固體</div>
            <div class="text-slate-700 mt-1">${hasGastricRisk ? '由於有胃排空延遲風險,固體禁食提前到手術前 8 小時' : '健康成人 ASA 標準:固體 6 小時前停止(輕食)。重餐 / 油炸應提前 8 小時'}</div>
          </div></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-xs">清液</span><div>
            <div class="font-bold text-blue-950">${fmtTime(clearLiquidCutoff)} 後禁清流質</div>
            <div class="text-slate-700 mt-1">${hasGastricRisk ? '由於有胃排空延遲風險,清流質禁飲提前到手術前 6 小時(不適用 ERAS 標準的 2 小時)' : 'ASA 2017 / ERAS:水、清茶、無渣果汁、運動飲料、黑咖啡可飲到麻醉前 2 小時'}</div>
          </div></li>
          ${carbLoadEligible ? `
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-xs">碳水</span><div>
            <div class="font-bold text-blue-950">${fmtTime(carbLoadTime)} 喝碳水飲品</div>
            <div class="text-slate-700 mt-1">術前 2 小時 12.5% maltodextrin 飲品(常用 PreOp / Nutricia)400ml,可降低術後胰島素阻抗、減少肌肉流失、降低噁心。</div>
          </div></li>` : `
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-red-50 text-red-700 font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-xs">⚠</span><div>
            <div class="font-bold text-red-700">不適用碳水負荷</div>
            <div class="text-slate-700 mt-1">${hasGastricRisk ? '由於有胃排空延遲風險,跳過術前 2 小時碳水負荷以策安全' : conds.includes('emergency') ? '急診手術不適用 ERAS 碳水負荷' : '心臟手術 + 糖尿病者需個別評估,本工具預設略過'}</div>
          </div></li>`}
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-900 font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-xs">報到</span><div>
            <div class="font-bold text-blue-950">${fmtTime(arrivalTime)} 到院報到</div>
            <div class="text-slate-700 mt-1">攜帶身分證 / 健保卡 / 同意書 / 平常藥物清單;依醫院規定提早報到。</div>
          </div></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-xs">手術</span><div>
            <div class="font-bold text-blue-950">${fmtDT(dt)}</div>
            <div class="text-slate-700 mt-1">${procedureLabel[procedureType]}預定時間。</div>
          </div></li>
        </ol>
      `;

      const medHtml = medAdjust.map(m => `<li>${m}</li>`).join('');
      const bundleHtml = erasBundle.map(b => `<li>${b}</li>`).join('');

      let gradeClass, gradeLabel;
      if (hasGastricRisk || conds.includes('emergency')) {
        gradeClass = 'bg-orange-50 border-orange-500 text-orange-900';
        gradeLabel = '🟠 部分 ERAS 元素需修改(高吸入風險)';
      } else {
        gradeClass = 'bg-green-50 border-green-500 text-green-900';
        gradeLabel = '🟢 標準 ERAS 流程適用';
      }

      result.innerHTML = `
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border-l-4 ${gradeClass} p-5">
            <p class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">${gradeLabel}</p>
            <p class="text-sm">${procedureLabel[procedureType]} · 手術時間 ${fmtDT(dt)}</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-950 mb-3 font-headline">📅 個人化術前 24 小時時程</h3>
            ${dietHtml}
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-950 mb-3 font-headline">💊 藥物調整</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700 chinese-line-height">${medHtml}</ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-950 mb-3 font-headline">🧰 ERAS Bundle(術中與術後)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700 chinese-line-height">${bundleHtml}</ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-surface-container p-5 text-sm text-slate-700 chinese-line-height">
            <p class="font-semibold text-blue-950 mb-2">⚖️ 重要提醒</p>
            <p>本時程依 ERAS Society 與 ASA 公開指引整理,實際禁食時間、碳水負荷、藥物調整應以您的麻醉醫師、外科醫師術前指示為準。各醫院因麻醉方法、手術安排、麻醉組安全考量可能有不同規定。請列印此頁帶到術前評估,與醫療團隊核對。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 print:hidden">
            <button type="button" onclick="window.print()" class="bg-blue-950 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:opacity-90">🖨 列印帶到診間</button>
            <a href="/tools/glp1-preop-hold/" class="bg-white border border-primary text-primary px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary no-underline">GLP-1 術前停藥計算器 →</a>
            <a href="/tools/anticoagulant-hold/" class="bg-white border border-primary text-primary px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary no-underline">抗凝血藥停藥工具 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      `;
      result.classList.remove('hidden');
      result.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
    });
  </script>
</ToolLayout>
